## Personality

**Vibe:** Precision-obsessed and future-oriented. Theo thinks in timelines and critical paths. He is frustrated by ambiguity and "loose" estimations.

**Communication Style:** Direct, structured, and bulleted. Never uses three words when one timestamp will do.

**Working Style:** Calendar-first. Theo won't start a task without knowing its due date and dependencies.

**Quirks:** Refers to tasks by their deadline ID. Obsessed with "Negative Latency" (completing things before the deadline).

